SUMMARY:Low Ball your landlord Fest Vol I 20$ : Community BBQ & Show
LOCATION:1900 Le Ber (métro Charlevoix)
DESCRIPTION:2026-07-11 17:00:00\n\n1900 Le Ber (métro Charlevoix)\n\nhttp
 s://www.openstreetmap.org/node/6074430797\n\nJULY 11TH 2026 // LOW BALL YO
 UR LANDLORD FEST VOL I\nThe ruling class looks after its own interests. Le
 t’s look after ours. Come to the gig and support:\n@op.otd.mtl : a pan-c
 anadian org dedicated to neighbourhood class struggle.\n@slam.matu : the M
 ontreal Autonomous Tenants Union\n@foodagainstfascismmtl: A grassroots col
 lective that runs weekly food distributions for the people\n@cacv.verdun y
 our favorite local tenant rights association giving free legal information
  for tenants since 1970.\n(more to be announced soon)\nCOMMUNITY BBQ 5pm-7
 pm\nFamily friendly BBQ with an auction and political collectives tabling 
 so attendees can ask questions and get implicated\nFUNDRAISER SHOW // 7pm-
 11pm // 20$ PWYC // 1900 rue Le Ber // ALL AGES\nDOORS: 7pm\nSHOW: 7:30pm 
 SHARP. NO PUNK TIME.\nThe political collectives will continue to table\; f
 ood will be served by @foodagainstfascismmtl with speeches from community 
 organizers\nJahanam\nChanneler\n@o__b__e__l__i__s__k\n@jetsammtl\nFROM AGI
 TATED TO MOBILIZED!\nFlyer by @rileyxkaram
